gov.lbl.glamm.server.retrosynthesis
Class Route

java.lang.Object
  gov.lbl.glamm.server.retrosynthesis.Route

public class Route
extends java.lang.Object

Class for conveniently representing routes between source and destination compounds. Includes accessory methods for pushing and popping route steps for convenient DFS implementations.

Author:
jtbates

Nested Class Summary
static class Route.RouteComparator
          Compares two routes by total cost.
static class Route.Step
          Route step assigning a cost to a node in the metabolic network (where a node includes both source and destination compound, as well as the reaction used to link the two.)
